contentrichtext.text: [[Image:Wahlkreis Kamanjab in Kunenea.png|thumb]] '''Kamanjab''' is a constituency in the [[Kunene Region]] of [[Namibia]]. In 2004, the population was 6,012.<ref>[http://www.statoids.com/yna.html Constituencies of Namibia, 2004]</ref> The district capital is the settlement of [[Kamanjab]]. The constituency is represented by [[Themistokles Dudu Murorua]] of the [[United Democratic Front (Namibia)|United Democratic Front]].<ref>[http://www.ecn.na/results/2010/Press_Release_Constituency_-_Kunene%20-%20Kamanjab.pdf Kamanjab Constituency] Electoral Commission of Namibia</ref> == References == {{reflist}} {{Constituencies of the Kunene Region}} {{Namibia-geo-stub}} {{coord|19|38|S|14|50|E|region:NA_type:city_source:eswiki|display=title}} [[Category:Constituencies of Kunene Region]]
